videos.description: Lagerald Vick drains the 3 from the wing to tie game at 5
videos.headline: Jayhawks bomb away early

videos.description: Josh Jackson hits 3 to increase Jayhawk lead to 12-7
videos.headline: Kansas' Jackson adds a 3 to KU lead

videos.description: Justin Bibbins just beats the shot clock and makes 3 to pull within 14-13
videos.headline: LBSU's Bibbins hits 3 at shot clock buzzer

videos.description: Vick keeps the ball alive and Devonte' Graham finishes from 3 as KU takes a 21-13 lead
videos.headline: Graham hits from top of key for 3

videos.description: Lagerald Vick makes the steal on one end and coast in for reverse dunk to give Jayhawks a 34-19 lead
videos.headline: KU's Vick with steal and reverse jam

videos.description: KU works the ball around and find Frank Mason III open for the 3 as Kansas now has 9 3's in the 1st half
videos.headline: Jayhawks stay hot from outside with Mason 3

videos.description: Devonte' Graham makes nice move to hoop and finishes a strong 1st half for Kansas
videos.headline: Jayhawks finish 1st half with flair on Graham layup

videos.description: Dwight Coleby takes pass from Mason and finishes strong
videos.headline: Jayhawks' Coleby finishes with 2 hand jam

videos.description: Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk made Three Point Jumper from corner as Kansas is now 13-18 from 3
videos.headline: Let it rain....Mykhailiuk with another Jayhawk 3

videos.description: With Kansas flying against Long Beach State, Udoka Azubuike gets in on the act with an alley-oop that leaves the hoop rattling.
videos.headline: Azubukie tries to pull down the rim on huge alley-oop
